                <MadCap:snippetText src="../Topics/OpenContentFileDocument.flsnp" />
            </li>
            <li>Place your cursor where you want to insert the snippet.</li>
            <li>
                <MadCap:snippetText src="../StepsGeneral/DoOneOfTheFollowingDependingOnUI.flsnp" />
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <p><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Ribbon </span>
                            <MadCap:snippetText src="../UIElements/SelectInsertRibbon.flsnp" /> In the <span class="Emphasis">Single Source</span> section select <span class="Emphasis">Snippet</span>. </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Local Toolbar</span> Click the face of the <img src="../../Images/insert_snippet_btn.png" alt="" title="" class="ReduceButtonSize" /> button.</p>
                        <p>OR</p>
                        <p>Click the down arrow next to <img src="../../Images/insert_snippet_btn.png" alt="" title="" class="ReduceButtonSize" />, then select <span class="Emphasis">More Snippets</span>.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Keyboard Shortcut</span> Press <span class="Emphasis">CTRL+R</span>.</li>
                    <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Right-Click </span>Right-click in the editor and select <span class="Emphasis">Insert&gt;Snippet</span>. This context menu option is available only when your cursor is located in certain places in the editor (e.g., not in a drop-down effect).</li>
                </ul>
                <p>The Insert Snippet Link dialog opens.</p>
            </li>
            <MadCap:snippetBlock src="../EmptyPageBreakAfter.flsnp" MadCap:conditions="FlareGuides.FlareSnippetsGuide" />
            <li>
                <p> <MadCap:snippetText src="SelectASnippet.flsnp" /></p>
                <p>
                    <img src="../../Images/insert_snippet_link_dialog.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth90Percent" />
                </p>
