                <MadCap:snippetBlock src="../UIElements/MultiViewTable2.flsnp" />
                <p class="note" MadCap:autonum="&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #70c0a9;&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatColor&quot;&gt;Note: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;">If you select a snippet file outside the project, that file is then copied and placed inside the project. The image file is stored in the Resources\Snippets folder of the Content Explorer.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <MadCap:snippetText src="../StepsGeneral/ClickOK.flsnp" /> The snippet is inserted and is surrounded by brackets (if markers are turned on).<p><img src="../../Images/snippet_examples.png" class="MaxWidth100Percent" /></p></li>
